🏏 Virat Kohli Test Career Analytics Report

📖 Business Summary
This project is a cricket analytics dashboard created to analyze Virat Kohli’s Test cricket career using SQL, Python, Excel, and Power BI. The dashboard provides opponent-wise and career-wise performance analysis through KPI reporting, milestone tracking, and batting pattern visualization.
The project transforms cricket statistics into meaningful analytical insights using data visualization and comparative performance analysis.

🎯 Objectives
Analyze Virat Kohli’s overall Test career statistics.
Compare performance against different opponents.
Evaluate batting consistency and scoring efficiency.
Track milestone achievements such as centuries and double centuries.
Analyze batting style using fours and sixes distribution.

