🔥 Key Findings

1️⃣ Best Performance – Sri Lanka
Highest Batting Average: 67.81
Highest Strike Rate: 68.28

Insight
Virat Kohli displayed highly aggressive yet consistent batting performance against Sri Lanka.

2️⃣ Toughest Opponent – Australia
Lowest Batting Average: 43.76
Highest Balls Faced: 4292

Insight
Australian bowling attacks demanded a more controlled and patient batting approach.

3️⃣ Batting Style Analysis
Total Fours: 1027
Total Sixes: 30

Insight
The boundary distribution highlights a technically strong and ground-shot focused Test batting style.

4️⃣ Consistency Analysis
Virat Kohli maintained strong batting performance across all major opponents without major performance collapse against any specific team.

